**This document is a template for a Prometheus integration document**: Please skim the entire template first to understand the expected structure for this type of doc. Then, clone this doc using the **Clone content** link in the **Page tools** box. Delete all content up to **Introduction (this heading won't be visible)**.

**For the doc title** (the field at top of page): Give your doc a practical name that is focused on the specific integration.

## Introduction (this heading will not be visible) [#intro]

Provide a brief explanation about why this document will be valuable for customers. Mention the key use cases, the customer value, the reason for using this integration, and when to use it.

## Requirements

Provide the versions we support.

Additional requirements on their own line (do not use bullets).

Do not use any callouts.

## Enable the integration

Write the steps to enable the integration beyond what is needed to install the Prometheus agent, if any.

