## Troubleshooting

Area for any common errors or troubleshooting tips.

<CollapserGroup>
  <Collapser
    id="error-name"
    title="Add an error name"
  >
    Indicate where the error appears.

    ### Solution:

    Add the instructions to know how to fix this error.

    ### Cause:

    Add a cause of the error: permits, requirements, etc.
  </Collapser>
</CollapserGroup>

### [Problem name]

Add a description of the problem.

### [Solution description]

Add steps to solve the problem.

### Step 1. Do something...

Add a description for this step.

### Step 2. Do something else...

Add a description for this step.
